overview:
Fashion Networks is a network of sites established in 2009 on the foundation of the increasing influence of bloggers. The network has a consolidated global reach of 5,5 million monthly unique visitors targeted at women age 15 – 35. The sites offer brands a dynamic advertising environment that drives results alongside content by today’s most influential voices. Their goal is relevance as well as reach.

Fashion Networks also creates exclusive advertising concepts and custom collaborations. They produce, design and execute in-house.
